OL,6,FSpecialist rape and sex offences
OL,7,Finvestigators will be introduced to
OL,8,Fevery police force as part of reforms
OL,9,Fto be introduced under the
OL,10,FGovernment's violence against women
OL,11,Fand girls (Vawg) strategy.
OL,13,FTeams to deal with such crimes will be
OL,14,Fset up by 2029 to replace an outdated
OL,15,Fsystem to better support victims and
OL,16,Fcrack down on rapists and sex
OL,17,Foffenders.
