OL,4,Cunder violence against women's strategy
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Home Secretary Shabana
OL,7,FMahmood has pledged to strip foreign
OL,8,Fsex offenders of refugee protections
OL,9,Fso that they can be deported faster
OL,10,Funder proposed reforms to human rights
OL,11,Flaws.
OL,13,FPlans will also be explored to widen a
OL,14,Fdisclosure scheme to allow for more
OL,15,Foffenders to have their past
OL,16,Fconvictions released to their partners
OL,17,Fon request.
OL,19,FShe announced the changes ahead of the
OL,20,FVawg strategy launch expected next
OL,21,Fweek.
