OL,6,FIt comes as ministers have vowed to
OL,7,Fhalve violence against women and girls
OL,8,Fin the next 10 years but have faced
OL,9,Fcriticism over delays to publishing
OL,10,Fthe plan.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, chairs of the Home Affairs
OL,13,FCommittee, Justice Committee and Women
OL,14,Fand Equalities Committee wrote to
OL,15,Fministers over concerns from Vawg
OL,16,Fgroups, including the delay is
OL,17,Fcreating "significant uncertainty"
OL,18,Facross the sector and sending a
OL,19,Fmessage Vawg is "not a government
OL,20,Fpriority".
