OL,6,FBut announcing the move, Home
OL,7,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood said: "This
OL,8,FGovernment has declared violence
OL,9,Fagainst women and girls a national
OL,10,Femergency.
OL,12,F"For too long, these crimes have been
OL,13,Fconsidered a fact of life.
OL,15,F"That's not good enough.
OL,17,F"We will halve it in a decade.
OL,19,F"Today we announce a range of measures
OL,20,Fto bear down on abusers, stopping them
OL,21,Fin their tracks.
