OL,6,F"Rapists, sex offenders and abusers
OL,7,Fwill have nowhere to hide."
OL,9,FUnder the strategy, domestic abuse
OL,10,Fprotection orders, which have been
OL,11,Ftrialled over the last year, will be
OL,12,Frolled out across England and Wales.
OL,14,FUnder the orders, courts can set
OL,15,Fconditions for as long as needed to
OL,16,Fprotect victims of all forms of
OL,17,Fdomestic abuse, including economic,
OL,18,Fcoercive behaviour, stalking and
OL,19,F"honour"-based violence.
