OL,6,FMs Mahmood is also proposing to reform
OL,7,Fhow Article 8 of the European
OL,8,FConvention on Human Rights ` the right
OL,9,Fto family and private life ` and
OL,10,FArticle 3 ` the right to freedom from
OL,11,Fdegrading treatment ` are applied.
OL,13,FThe definition of "family connection"
OL,14,Fis to be tightened to prevent distant
OL,15,Frelationships being cited in
OL,16,Fchallenges to deportations.
