OL,6,FMs Mahmood told the Sunday Telegraph
OL,7,Fthat "for too long, the human rights
OL,8,Fof foreign sex offenders have been
OL,9,Fprioritised over the safety of British
OL,10,Fwomen and girls".
OL,12,F"We will introduce new laws to make
OL,13,Fthis country and its citizens safer,
OL,14,Fensuring perpetrators of sexual
OL,15,Fviolence are swiftly removed from
OL,16,FBritish soil," she said.
