OL,6,FThe Home Secretary will also explore
OL,7,Fexpanding the domestic violence
OL,8,Fdisclosure scheme, also known as
OL,9,FClare's Law, so that more perpetrators
OL,10,Fof abuse have their past convictions
OL,11,Freleased on request.
OL,13,FThe Government is considering widening
OL,14,Fthe scheme to include other forms of
OL,15,Fviolence such as sexual assault,
OL,16,Fstalking and harassment.
