OL,6,FMs Mahmood told the Mirror the plans
OL,7,Fmust begin with "making sure no woman
OL,8,Fis left in the dark not knowing if the
OL,9,Fpartner she is with has a history of
OL,10,Fviolence or abuse".
OL,12,F"We will consult on the changes so
OL,13,Fwomen can have more power and control
OL,14,Fover their own safety," she told the
OL,15,Fpaper.
OL,17,FMs Mahmood told The Sun on Sunday "the
OL,18,Flatest" counter-terror style
OL,19,Ftechnology will also be deployed by
OL,20,Fpolice to target rapists and stalkers.
